HEADWORD: Fermentative
<hw>Fer*ment"a*tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>fermentatif</ets>.]</ety> <def>Causing, or having power to cause,
fermentation; produced by fermentation; fermenting; <as>as, a
<ex>fermentative</ex> process</as>.</def></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Fer*ment"a*tive*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Fer*ment"a*tive*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fermenter</ent>⟦br⟧
